title: ModuleNotFoundError Example
description: Demonstrate a ModuleNotFoundError (importing a non-existent module).
instructions:
Run the code. You should see:
```
Traceback (most recent call last):
  File "module_not_found_error.py", line 1, in <module>
    import not_a_real_module
ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'not_a_real_module'
```
